IZIDLELE  amahlanga kumaSafta (South African Television and Film Awards) ifilimu Inxeba (The Wound), esanda kubuyiselwa emabhayisikobho ngemuva kokugxekwa ngeziqephu zocansi nokuveza izinto ezithathwa njengemfihlo yalabo abasuke beyosoka entabeni emaXhoseni. Le filimu iwole izindondo ezinhlanu emcimbini wokuhlonipha amaciko ngeqhaza lawo kwezokungcebeleka kuleli obuseSun City Superbowl, eNorth West, izolo. Lo mcimbi osakazwe bukhoma kuSABC2 izolo ebusuku, uthulwe ngosaziwayo uThando Thabethe noPhat Joe. Inxeba liwadlisele ogageni amanye amafilimu njengoba liqokwe njengefilimu evelele emunxeni iBest Feature Film. Umdidiyeli walo uJohn Trengove uwine indondo yokuba ngumdidiyeli ovelele kumunxa iBest Achievement in Directing-Feature Film. Iphinde yaphuma phambili kwiBest Achievement in Scriptwriting-Feature Film, lapho ekutuswe amagalelo kaJohn Trevonge, Malusi Bengu noThando Mgqolozana. Umlingisi oqavile wale filimu uNakhare odlala indawo kaXolani, uklonyeliswe ngendondo yokuba ngumlingisi wesilisa oqavile kumunxa iBest Actor-Feature Film. UBongile Mantsai odlala indawo kaVija uwine indondo yeBest Supporting Actor-Feature Film. Emikhomelweni yangoLwesihlanu uMatthew Swanepoel, uwine indondo kwiBest Editing-Feature Film. Izintokazi zaseMgungundlovu zibuye zihleka zodwa njengoba uJo-anne Reyneke odlala indawo kaThandi kwiBroken Vows ewine iBest Actress-TV Soap/Telenovela, kwathi uThuso Mbedu wawina iBest Actress-TV Drama ngokudlala indawo kaWinnie kumdlalo Isâ€™thunzi. Abanye abawinile kubalwa: 1. Best Actor-TV Comedy uMandla Gaduka odlala indawo kaSolomon kwiGauteng Maboneng. 2. Best Supporting Actress-TV Comedy uLinda Sebezo odlala indawo kaGogo kwiGauteng Maboneng. 3. Best Achievement in Directing-TV Soap/ Telenovela abadidiyeli be-Isibaya uPhiwe Mkhanzi noSthembiso Mathenjwa. 4. Best Actor-TV Soap/Telenovela uHamilton Dhlamini odlala indawo kaBanzi Motaung kumdlalo Isithembiso. 5. Best Supporting Actor-TV Soap/Telenovela uPallance Dladla odlala indawo kaJabu Zungu ngodlalo Isibaya. 6. Best TV Soap- Isibaya 7. Best Achievement in Directing -TV Drama uCatherine Cooke, Rolie Nikiw noRea Rangaka iNumber Number. 8. Best Achievement in Scriptwriting -TV Drama, Lockdown,  Reabetswe Moeti noMandla Ngcongwane 9. Best Actor -TV Drama uWarren Masemola odlala uMa Fred kwiTjovitjo 10. Best TV Drama iTjovitjo. 11. Best Talk Show Host, Pabi Moloi weTrending SA. Kushaye isikhathi sokushicilela ingakaphumi imiphumela yeBest TV Presenter neMost Popular TV Soap/ Telenovela njengoba bekuyiminxa ebivotelwa.                